  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/2d39cfafa0a8bf0e8b76fc5de6ff6c17.poster.avif?t=1740311572\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/2d39cfafa0a8bf0e8b76fc5de6ff6c17.webm?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/2d39cfafa0a8bf0e8b76fc5de6ff6c17.mp4?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A turn-based roguelike where skills have a probability of getting executed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/4fa052795b76f449934721e90ac6fc6e.poster.avif?t=1740311572\" width=150 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/4fa052795b76f449934721e90ac6fc6e.webm?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/4fa052795b76f449934721e90ac6fc6e.mp4?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/1292751cccbed1603fd5d6ce8d05d231.poster.avif?t=1740311572\" width=150 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/1292751cccbed1603fd5d6ce8d05d231.webm?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/1292751cccbed1603fd5d6ce8d05d231.mp4?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your characters have an ordered list of skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every turn, you will need to decide the skill order to adapt to the enemy intents. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/39797626d099c3688afb0814d8a4f740.poster.avif?t=1740311572\" width=432 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/39797626d099c3688afb0814d8a4f740.webm?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/39797626d099c3688afb0814d8a4f740.mp4?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through the game, you will need to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add, replace or improve skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip accessories to characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt and establish different strategies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For this, you will have to look for shops, try the different events that you will find throughout the map or gain fight rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/ffbe32d67e3040421a617aa9e9e3e7b7.avif?t=1740311572\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras_big/ffbe32d67e3040421a617aa9e9e3e7b7.avif?t=1740311572 width=800 height=312 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Characters to combine, with different game styles and skill pools</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+150 Skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+80 Accessories</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/2d39cfafa0a8bf0e8b76fc5de6ff6c17.poster.avif?t=1740311572\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/2d39cfafa0a8bf0e8b76fc5de6ff6c17.webm?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/2d39cfafa0a8bf0e8b76fc5de6ff6c17.mp4?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A turn-based roguelike where skills have a probability of getting executed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/4fa052795b76f449934721e90ac6fc6e.poster.avif?t=1740311572\" width=150 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/4fa052795b76f449934721e90ac6fc6e.webm?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/4fa052795b76f449934721e90ac6fc6e.mp4?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/1292751cccbed1603fd5d6ce8d05d231.poster.avif?t=1740311572\" width=150 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/1292751cccbed1603fd5d6ce8d05d231.webm?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/1292751cccbed1603fd5d6ce8d05d231.mp4?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your characters have an ordered list of skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every turn, you will need to decide the skill order to adapt to the enemy intents. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/39797626d099c3688afb0814d8a4f740.poster.avif?t=1740311572\" width=432 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/39797626d099c3688afb0814d8a4f740.webm?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/39797626d099c3688afb0814d8a4f740.mp4?t=1740311572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through the game, you will need to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add, replace or improve skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip accessories to characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt and establish different strategies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For this, you will have to look for shops, try the different events that you will find throughout the map or gain fight rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras/ffbe32d67e3040421a617aa9e9e3e7b7.avif?t=1740311572\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215240/extras_big/ffbe32d67e3040421a617aa9e9e3e7b7.avif?t=1740311572 width=800 height=312 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Characters to combine, with different game styles and skill pools</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+150 Skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+80 Accessories</p></li></ul>",
